commands: jq --arg buildroot "$FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR" --argjson data '{"github:supershabam/nop": "flatpak-node/git-packages/nop-f110e75f62cfe3bf4468ac3b74e3dc72ab9ae4bf#f110e75f62cfe3bf4468ac3b74e3dc72ab9ae4bf"}' 'walk(    if type == "object"    then        to_entries | map(            if (.value | type == "string") and $data[.value]            then .value = "git+file:\($buildroot)/\($data[.value])"            else .            end        ) | from_entries    else .    end)' $FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR/flatpak-builder-tools/node/tests/data/packages/minimal-git/package.json > $FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR/flatpak-builder-tools/node/tests/data/packages/minimal-git/package.json.new
